        "data": "<h1 id=\"01H8066N1X71BMWR8KPQVMTM4A\">Service Updates for Liferay Cloud</h1>\n\n<p>The services update for&nbsp;<strong>2025-09-02</strong>&nbsp;includes a&nbsp;<strong>patch</strong>&nbsp;update for <strong>CI</strong>, <strong>Database</strong>, <strong>Search</strong> and<strong> Webserver&nbsp;</strong>services.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"01H8066N1X678XQSM8P38E9Q5Z\">DXP Cloud Stack&nbsp;</h2>\n\n<table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; border-color: #f7f8f9; border-spacing: 0px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; width: 100%;\">\n\t<colgroup>\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 16%;\" />\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 14%;\" />\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 13%;\" />\n\t\t<col style=\"width: 57%;\" />\n\t</colgroup>\n\t<thead>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 62px;\">\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); height: 62px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; width: 84.8px;\"><strong>Service Name</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); height: 62px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; width: 68.3px;\"><strong>Previous Release</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); height: 62px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; width: 61.2833px;\"><strong>Current Release</strong></th>\n\t\t\t<th style=\"background-color: rgb(150, 153, 150); height: 62px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; width: 377.617px;\"><strong>Docker Images</strong></th>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</thead>\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 48px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 84.8px;\">Backup</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 68.3px;\">5.25.1</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 61.2833px;\">5.25.2</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; width: 377.617px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li data-list-item-id=\"e36c68276b10a9ec192d98603daa472d9\">liferaycloud/backup:5.25.2</li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 36px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 84.8px;\"><strong>CI</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 68.3px;\"><strong>6.1.0</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 61.2833px;\"><strong>6.1.1</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; width: 377.617px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"e29a6115cee5e1b4a0c5e0fdaab934153\"><strong>liferaycloud/jenkins:2.492.3-lts-jdk21-6.1.1</strong></li>\n\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr style=\"height: 41.2222px;\">\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 84.8px;\"><strong>Database</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 68.3px;\"><strong>5.7.2</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: center; vertical-align: top; width: 61.2833px;\"><strong>5.7.3</strong></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"background-color: rgb(247, 248, 249); height: 10px; padding: 0.75rem; text-align: left; vertical-align: top; width: 377.617px;\">\n\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t<li class=\"ck-list-marker-bold\" data-list-item-id=\"ef72d36